                                  <a class="link" href="https://oshwiki.eu/wiki/Engineering_controls" target="_blank">Tæknilegar ráðstafarnir, eins og niðurbrot</a><br />
                                  <a class="link" href="https://oshwiki.eu/wiki/Hierarchy_of_prevention_and_control_measures" target="_blank">Skipulagsráðstafanir, eins og niðurskipting starfsstöðva</a><br />
                                  <a class="link" href="https://oshwiki.eu/wiki/PPE" target="_blank">Persónulegur hlífðarbúnaður</a>
                                </p></div></div></div></div></div>

                      <div class="nid-1 views-row" data-id="1"><div class="views-field views-field-body"><div class="field-content"><div class="row"><div class="col-4">  <img src="/{{ base_path ~ directory }}/images/external-infographic-images/dangerous-menage.png" width="219" height="292" alt="" typeof="Image" />


                              </div><div class="col-8"><h2>Stjórnun hættulegra efna <a class="info-link" href="https://oshwiki.eu/wiki/Dangerous_substances_(chemical_and_biological)" target="_blank"><img alt="info" src="/{{ base_path ~ directory }}/images/external-infographic-images/info.png" /></a></h2>
